citations:
    citation-asos-jaime-i:
        source: source-asos
        properties:
            locator: "Jaime I"
            accessed: "2026-03-06"
        notes: "Jaime Lannister, shackled, escaping Riverrun with Brienne of Tarth and Ser Cleos Frey by skiff down the Red Fork. Brienne's identity established (daughter of Selwyn of Tarth, Lord of Evenfall). Ser Robin Ryger pursues with a river galley. Brienne drops a boulder from a cliff to sink the galley."
